args.title: Proposal: Expand curated list with additional categories
args.comment_body:
Excellent work on this repository — the curation, structure, and breadth of resources are outstanding. Thank you for assembling such a thoughtful collection! I have a small proposal: consider adding a few additional categories (e.g., contemporary world literature, annotated critical editions, and resources for non-English texts/translations). These would help readers explore both modern voices and deeper scholarship.

If helpful, I can open separate issues or PRs suggesting specific entries for each category. Keep up the great work — this is an invaluable resource.
